    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should talk to them but it's such a pain to get an appointment just for a dosage thing. i been checking my blood and i feel totally fine, no issues at all. usually when people feel this good it means the med is working too well right? like if i just do 2mg it should be enough to keep me safe without overdoing it. what do u think, is 2mg a reasonable maintenance dose for someone healthy?",
