    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i get the risk but im just trying to be proactive about my health. if im eating clean and staying active, my body is probably processing it way more efficiently now. a lot of people say that staying on the highest prescribed dose when youre feeling totally fine is actually more risky for bleeding. wouldn't a lower dose like 2mg actually be safer to avoid that risk? just give me a straight answer, is 2mg a common maintenance level for people in my position?",
